data.description:
Completely refurbished 2 BR/2.5 BA town house in West Augusta. Very nice end unit with all new Kitchen cabinetry, appliances, and fixtures. New LVP flooring, carpet, and fresh paint throughout the home. HVAC approx. 3 years old. The two bedrooms are on the second level, each with their own full bath. There is a half bath located on the main floor as well. A nice rear deck overlooks the spacious fenced in back yard. Great for grilling, entertaining or just relaxing.
Must see to appreciate!
